            .row
                .col-1#homeBanner
                    h1 Magic Mind
                    h4 This site is designed to provide meditation aids. So when you are stuck at home or in your office and you need to relieve stress, you can gaze at your monitor and it will help to empty your mind. You can then either meditate or just relax and reduce your stress.
            .row
                .col-1
                    h2 Beaches
                    p Close your eyes and imagine yourself on a beach. With the warm sun on your face. The air feels moist and embracing. You can hear the sound of seagulls calling and the rhythmic lapping of the waves on the shore. Your feel wonderfully relaxed and free. Small and yet at peace next to the ocean. Choose a picture that you like and click on it to enlarge it. Look at the photo and imagine yourself on the beach.
